flavoredCookies.name: Cashew cookies
flavoredCookies.description: Let me tell you about cashews. Cashews are not nuts, but seeds that grow out of curious red or yellow fruits - which can be eaten on their own, or made into drinks. The shell around the nut itself contains a nasty substance that stains and irritates the hands of whoever handles it for too long. But that's okay, since now that you've read this you'll make sure it doesn't get into the cookies! Oh, you've already eaten how many? Okay then.
